    <MissileTemplate>
      <Designation>SGT-350</Designation>
      <Nickname>SUN FISH</Nickname>
      <Description>$MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT - &lt;color=#D3D11F&gt;$MISSILESEEKER_MODE_COMMAND_ABBREV&lt;/color&gt;/$MISSILESEEKER_MODE_SEMIACTIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;RADAR&lt;/color&gt;) - $MISSILEWARHEAD_SHORT_HEIMPACT</Description>
      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGT-350 SUN FISH&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGT-3 body, which is a heavy anti-ship torpedo.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Semi-Active Radar seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE: &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_POS&lt;/color&gt;	&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRACK&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;

