      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGT-300 EEL&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGT-3 body, which is a heavy anti-ship torpedo.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker, validating that it is the correct target using command guidance from its launching ship.

